<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Trebuchet MS', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding: 10px; color: #0890b2;">Welcome to Goto College in US, <span style="color:#333"><%= @page[:name] %></span></h1>
    <p style="padding:5px 15px;font-size:18px;line-height:28px; text-align:justify">
      Your request for the page " <%= @page[:title] %> " has been approved for creation and publication, please take a note of the App Key sent along with this mail. Follow the link below and use the given App Key for the Page Creation Process.</p>
    <p style="padding:10px 15px;font-size:22px;color: #0890b2;">App Key : <%= @page[:key] %></p>
    <% if @page[:d] == "show" %>
    <p style="padding:5px 15px;font-size:18px;">
      Note : <%= @page[:n] %>
    </p>
    <% end %>
    <p style="padding:5px 15px;font-size:18px;">
      To continue with the page, just follow this link: http://localhost:3000/page/verify/
    </p>
    <p style="padding:5px 15px;font-size:18px; color:#222">Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html> 